{"tid":2225881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐取暖] 個人好辛苦","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T09:56:10.000Z","uid":355267,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9b583256791f288c050d4f6f5aa21ecab16b011c","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，之前做開cd-rom，如果有錯，希望各位屌得細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近好辛苦，雖然返工個陣無咩野，但係返工之前同收工之後個人都好唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都好想喊，但係喊完都唔會覺得有種舒服d既感覺<br />\n個心'浪著浪著'，好似吊係到咁，一d都唔安落<br />\n同埋胃口都差左<br />\n個情況會係個人獨處同到夜晚個陣加劇<br />\n想睇書又睇唔到，覺得理解唔到入面到底寫緊咩<br />\n想寫下野都寫唔到，個腦空白一片<br />\n但好彩打fgo、睇下片、上下連登都叫做到，令自己分散到注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時候會有種好強烈想傷害自己既念頭<br />\n但老實講我又唔會做得出，因為仲有兩老同貓貓係到，唔想佢地傷心，同埋最大既牽挂都係貓貓佢地，前排要手術無返屋企一排，返到屋企，聽到屋企人話我唔係到個幾日，佢地都好似唔開心咁，唔係點肯玩，係我返到黎之後，佢地有返精神，我就覺得點都唔可以走得快過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道壓力來源於返工，所以都去左搵工，同埋見左工，雖然覺得個表現唔係幾好，但好好醜醜都趁有精神個陣努力過，希望都可以轉到去新地方，雖然到時應該又會有其他問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過覺得自己完左依家個份工既約都唔會想繼續做啦<br />\n其實我都知自己應該去求醫，但係又覺得未係時候，不過真係捱唔著個陣我都會去a&amp;e<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人又毒，又無咩朋友，雖然同朋友講過下個情況，而佢都理解我個情況、都肯陪著我、安慰我，但又覺得無謂令佢咁擔心，始終佢都有佢既生活要過<br />\n所以好想向大家取暖，好想搵人抱下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果朋友你見到呢個post，我想同你講：<br />\n好多謝你成日聽我叫春，我真係好開心可以識到你<br />\n我都會努力咁繼續生存落去<br />\n但係如果有一日我真係做左傻事，希望你都唔好咁自責，你已經盡左能力做左你可以做既野啦<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3fb47902e3038022c66d7c3e8ed76a0a79b860","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都驚放負放得太多 <br />\n搞到人地唔知點比反應"},{"pid":"235a7573e0c28216345680d2df4f5941b0e47d8f","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a3fb47902e3038022c66d7c3e8ed76a0a79b860","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都驚放負放得太多 <br />\n搞到人地唔知點比反應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"抱抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明啊，所以先唔敢講咁多，自己收收埋埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f26e6cad6466ea9bee3f6202bc2991a1f45e797","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235a7573e0c28216345680d2df4f5941b0e47d8f","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a3fb47902e3038022c66d7c3e8ed76a0a79b860","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都驚放負放得太多 <br />\n搞到人地唔知點比反應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"抱抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明啊，所以先唔敢講咁多，自己收收埋埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"同網友講下 學下隔離post啲人留tg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總有人會肯聽"},{"pid":"177c731b9b278e66d7c03c134f4e9e2094eb8fab","tid":2225881,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"唉呢排好唔知應該做乜 太多問題<br />\n<br />\n加油 好唔容易 但總會雨過天清"},{"pid":"5908de9e51b5fed84a224097115ef9429801ee9b","tid":2225881,"uid":92859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HRlgIzj9wmI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHRlgIzj9wmI&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w14R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9239660e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HRlgIzj9wmI</a><br />\n<br />\n失望　不安　你怎麼了？<br />\n有著陽光般燦爛笑容的你　到哪裡去了？<br />\n<br />\n想做的事情　現在就去做　這才是青春<br />\n<br />\n難過的時候　我永遠　都會在你身邊<br />\n<br />\n夢想如果不『狂妄』一點　那多沒意思<br />\n讓我們拍拍胸脯　去冒險<br />\n<br />\n對呀　用 100% 的勇氣　現在能做到的只有更努力嘛<br />\n懷抱這世界上　所有的元氣<br />\n<br />\n對呀 用 100% 的勇氣　現在能做到的只有盡力<br />\n請你永遠不要忘記　我們所擁有的光芒<br />\n又是碰傷　又是創傷　做的話還是比較好嘛<br />\n<br />\n如果你熱情似火　就不要畏懼<br />\n原地不動的話 就無法啟動　心中那份悸動<br />\n我喜歡　能夠追隨你的腳步而去的風<br />\n<br />\n如果　昨天沒能翱翔的天空還存在<br />\n那就讓我們　抓住現在的機會<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣　用 100% 的勇氣　來吧　飛向那裡<br />\n現在　還不是只靠流淚就能結束的時候<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣 用 100% 的勇氣　已經不能再回頭<br />\n我們　要以我們的風采　到任何地方<br />\n<br />\n即使　寂寞的夜晚將要來臨<br />\n新的早晨　也必將到來<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣　用 100% 的勇氣　現在能做到的只有努力<br />\n懷抱這世界上　所有的勇氣<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣　用 100% 的勇氣　現在能做到的只有盡力<br />\n<br />\n請你永遠不要忘記　我們所擁有的光芒"},{"pid":"07fa97cc510448b880175481d3d8f758f878dd47","tid":2225881,"uid":260232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又圍下爐先"},{"pid":"9e869671db7c0ab355b2760d74b110a95acba747","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f26e6cad6466ea9bee3f6202bc2991a1f45e797","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235a7573e0c28216345680d2df4f5941b0e47d8f","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a3fb47902e3038022c66d7c3e8ed76a0a79b860","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"hug <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都驚放負放得太多 <br />\n搞到人地唔知點比反應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"抱抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明啊，所以先唔敢講咁多，自己收收埋埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"同網友講下 學下隔離post啲人留tg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總有人會肯聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"謝謝你既提意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實本身個人毒，又唔係點識同人講野，打開話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係都會努力試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c63993ef829894a393b9b86700e4d74c6939cec","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"177c731b9b278e66d7c03c134f4e9e2094eb8fab","tid":2225881,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"唉呢排好唔知應該做乜 太多問題<br />\n<br />\n加油 好唔容易 但總會雨過天清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"黎抱下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你都要加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206bd44babd7900a80f3e9abf1d4df2cbdfa2ef9","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07fa97cc510448b880175481d3d8f758f878dd47","tid":2225881,"uid":260232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又圍下爐先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"圍下爐暖d咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db150a88cb64a35f9007e9b3c27b90e09062ff40","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi