 />\n返工嗰陣就煩返工<br />\n人生就係不斷受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"好想引用返工台金句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返工返到人生完左架啦！完左架啦！上帝都沒法攙扶架啦！唔死一身潺呀 ！好地地一個人生咁就完左架啦！<br />\n我唔識做架！唔好罵我呀！！！我要返屋企呀！！<br />\n真的想哭！真的想哭！返工怎會一臉笑容<br />\n<br />\n你地知唔知呀！！！我每一日係返工路上，都好想捉住每一個路人講：我返工返到人生完左架啦！！！ 你知唔知呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n返工返到人生等死咁。真係玩完。<br />\n要等死架啦。等死架啦。<br />\n我人生要完啦!! 我唔想完呀 !!! 但係冇得唔完呀 !!!"},{"pid":"d316d79c0167dd4c5ad8ef03c09af68c2238d64c","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db150a88cb64a35f9007e9b3c27b90e09062ff40","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e869671db7c0ab355b2760d74b110a95acba747","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f26e6cad6466ea9bee3f6202bc2991a1f45e797","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"同網友講下 學下隔離post啲人留tg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總有人會肯聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"謝謝你既提意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實本身個人毒，又唔係點識同人講野，打開話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係都會努力試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係 如果想搵絲打傾 又要諗點樣打開話題吸引佢覆<br />\n其實仲煩<br />\n<br />\n如果唔介意呢到傾啲 都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"好啊，多謝你，如果你唔介意我覆得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7be33c527cd532526d94f6919e47badbc1cf683","tid":2225881,"uid":289152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d316d79c0167dd4c5ad8ef03c09af68c2238d64c","tid":2225881,"uid":355267,"li